  34,3,"BoniayŒµfoÕª no ka sŒµ: ‚ÄúDÕªnhwere no mma yŒµn so biara‚Äù. KasŒµ: ‚Äò‚ÄôAane, Mede me Wura, AhuntasŒµm mu NimdefoÕª no di nse sŒµ, ŒµbŒµba mo so. DeŒµ emu duro ketekete tesŒµ aboboaa a (onipa) ani ntumi nhunu wÕª soro anaasŒµ asaase so anaasŒµ deŒµ esua kyŒµn saa anaasŒµ deŒµ Œµso kyŒµn saa mmpa ne ho, na mmom (nenyinaa) wÕª Nwoma pefee no mu"
